  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK781">
<l>ceyaṟkariya yāvuḷa naṭpi ṉatupōl</l>
<l>viṉaikkariya yāvuḷa kāppu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>What things are there so difficult to acquire as friendship ? What guards are there so difficult to break through by the efforts (of one's foes) ?</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
